{"tid":2054450,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"多圖｜ 《嚇鬼女朋友》國民初戀Ploy　跟BLACKPINK Lisa泰似樣！","createTime":"2020-06-07T07:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T08:16:09.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b232fd9bee9dc4951e240991944ff8794e760641","tid":2054450,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:23:28.000Z","msg":"泰國電影《嚇鬼女朋友》（Low Season）集愛情、搞笑及驚慄於一身，由泰國男神Mario Maurer同泰國國民初戀Ploypailin Thangprapaporn擔正主演，Ploy今年只得22歲，在戲中愈看愈耐看，加上有幾分似韓國人氣女團BLACKPINK泰國成員Lisa的關係，令她的話題度更度攀升。<br />\n<br />\nPloy今次在戲中飾演一位擁有陰陽眼的平凡女生，跟巨星男友分手後，決定趁着淡季遠離城市，去到清邁一所民宿渡假散心，來個失戀療傷之旅。<br />\n<br />\n但就在旅途中遇上來郊區尋找鬼片靈感的編劇Pud（Mario 飾），兩人不打不相識，意外地走在一起，展開了一連串撞鬼冒險，更在不知不覺間互相治療，普出愛歌。<br />\n<br />\nPloy樣子甜美可愛，在戲中有失魂、傷心、爆喊、可愛一面。今年才22歲，演出過《我宿舍的壞蛋》、《新魚之戀》、《交火》、《麻辣情缘》等泰劇。Ploy IG的追蹤者足有近35萬人數，是泰國公認的「國民初戀」，她自言是位攝影家和旅行家，更開設個人YouTube頻道，不時都會有影片更新，更會自彈自唱，彈結他都難不到她，認真多才多藝！"},{"pid":"af7981185b36f19011b801c0c0ca0a07ef3c2ad9","tid":2054450,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200606/345908563698388992.jpeg/v-9I4pnwijn4YUfjIDdsffebRv2Ww6VDI-zB1yPswdc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200606%2F345908563698388992.jpeg%2Fv-9I4pnwijn4YUfjIDdsffebRv2Ww6VDI-zB1yPswdc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=07ab9455&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200606/345912953494704128.jpeg/tT6WzbAf6QdcsxmMrqRbZCi1YHRWbyeCgGhUlYBoVJU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200606%2F345912953494704128.jpeg%2FtT6WzbAf6QdcsxmMrqRbZCi1YHRWbyeCgGhUlYBoVJU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=232e4b7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f9ee91479b0fe1a9a3e7a09e87e04aa3c3ae273","tid":2054450,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk